malnourished; no one thing can sustain the

00:02:38.410 --> 00:02:39.819
human body -- we need a variety of things.

00:02:39.819 --> 00:02:42.293
An apple (or pear or other fruit or vegetable)
may keep the doctor away, but it's not going

00:02:42.293 --> 00:02:43.293
